  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Little is known about efficacy of switching to tenofovir monotherapy for lam-resistant
      chronic hepatitis B patients who achieved a complete virological response to lamivudine plus
      adefovir. This study was to investigate the efficacy of switching to tenofovir monotherapy
      for lamivudine -resistant chronic hepatitis B patients with undetectable hepatitis B virus
      DNA while on lamivudine plus adefovir combination therapy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
